item.title: Anyway to log in runescape 2 accs same world
item.dc:creator: @deoxys505 deoxys505
item.description:
@deoxys505 wrote:

[quote=“3.65 kilos, post:2, topic:141293”]Easier way:

First, open up two windows for your browser. Have both windows go to the Runescape “Detail select” page.

On one window, just choose low detail and choose a world. Log in.

Second window, scroll down to the drop down box and choose the bottom option (Unsigned Java Applet). Then choose low detail and log into the same world as your other account.[/quote]
